  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ragdoll is fun! </h2>In this game, you can launch your character anywhere, watching as his limbs dangle and hit all the obstacles.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1524400/extras/ed6b083e03a91374729b9d532b165667.poster.avif?t=1656960101\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1524400/extras/ed6b083e03a91374729b9d532b165667.webm?t=1656960101\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1524400/extras/ed6b083e03a91374729b9d532b165667.mp4?t=1656960101\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Goals? Tasks? Meaning?</h2> Not. Nothing limits you in the game. Choose any level and do what you want!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Everything is dynamic! Even the game menu :D<br></li><li>Realistic collision simulation<br></li><li>Many cool levels<br></li><li>Dynamic objects<br></li><li>Random characters<br></li><li>Detailed physics settings [optional]<br></li><li>Freedom to experiment</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Feel free to turn on any level and try it!</h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ragdoll is fun! </h2>In this game, you can launch your character anywhere, watching as his limbs dangle and hit all the obstacles.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1524400/extras/ed6b083e03a91374729b9d532b165667.poster.avif?t=1656960101\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1524400/extras/ed6b083e03a91374729b9d532b165667.webm?t=1656960101\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1524400/extras/ed6b083e03a91374729b9d532b165667.mp4?t=1656960101\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Goals? Tasks? Meaning?</h2> Not. Nothing limits you in the game. Choose any level and do what you want!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Everything is dynamic! Even the game menu :D<br></li><li>Realistic collision simulation<br></li><li>Many cool levels<br></li><li>Dynamic objects<br></li><li>Random characters<br></li><li>Detailed physics settings [optional]<br></li><li>Freedom to experiment</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Feel free to turn on any level and try it!</h2>",
